        Installation
        ------------
        
        POP-tools can be installed from PyPI with pip:
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            pip install pop-tools
        
        
        It is also available from `conda-forge` for conda installations:
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            conda install -c conda-forge pop-tools
        
